<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Shriek1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Shriek,</orth> subst. a sharp outcry, a scream: <bibl n="shak. wt 3.3.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 3, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 2, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 4.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 3, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.168" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 168</bibl>. cf. <emph>Night-shriek.</emph>
